  "title": "Dirty Little Secrets",
  "description": "Time to spill the tea. In Dirty Little Secrets, we read your nasty lil’ confessions to craft improv comedy gold. Witness the scandalous, anonymous, hilarious show that lets you bare your darkest secrets and guiltiest sins to a room full of strangers – at a fraction of the price of therapy.",
  "credits": "<strong>Cast</strong>: Joleen Ballendine, Chris Borger, Quinn Contini, Julian Faid, Marg Lawler, Gordie Lucius, Sarah Mattiello, Dill Prusko, Sam Stralak, Marielle Terhart and Kelly Turner<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "People send us their secret confessions. These are things they feel guilty or bad about. We don't say who sent them. Then, funny people make up jokes about these secrets. This makes a funny show. You can hear surprising and silly stories. It's like everyone is sharing secrets and laughing together. It costs less money than talking to a doctor about your feelings. This show was created by a group named Momentous Comedy.",
